This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.DL (Digital Libraries) as it deals with the availability of free full-text articles on the web. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves searching for and accessing articles. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it deals with the security of online content. It could also be classified under cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it involves analyzing and processing text data. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it deals with the impact of open access on the dissemination of knowledge.
